name: Rubix Pyramid Cube
description: 3X3 Speed Triangle Rubik Pyraminx Puzzle Cube

name: VeryPuzzle Clover
description: The VeryPuzzle Clover Icosahedron D1 is the 20-sided variant of the Clover Cube. As with the other clover cube variants, it features 2 locations on each edge that can be rotated freely. With professional design adjustments and molding technology, this cube has attained a smoother feeling and better performance, while being an overall outstanding cube!

name: Roulette Wheel Rubik
description: Ready for your left and right brain training? This Roulette Wheel Rubik cube will be the hardest cube challenge in your cube solving journey. There are 6 color surface, 6 roulette wheels with numbers on it. To solve this cube firstly you may need to match each roulette color and sequence numbers and then each surface color.

name: Ghost Cube
description: If you are a fan of DC universe you are going to love this thing. Ghost Cube is a savior for those who are not into stickers and colors. Get the darker side of your brain unleashed through this environment-friendly Rubik's cube that is only black and white.

name: Windmill Rubik’s cube
description: We all know looks can be deceptive when it comes to humans but do you know that it’s true for Rubik’s cube also? Well, Windmill Rubik’s cube may look like a regular 3*3 cube, but it is nothing like that. It can be solved in two ways that make it attractive to the eyes.

name: Circular Rubik’s Cube
description: Give the puzzle enthusiast within you a challenge of his lifetime with Circular Rubik’s Cube. The cube is an exception to the cubic community for it’s not a cube, but a ball-like structure with a colorful appearance. This cube also promises to be a valuable addition to your work desk for its aesthetic value.

name: Simple Rubik's Cube
description: If the regular puzzle is too mind-boggling for you then why not give this simple Rubik’s cube a try! Challenge yourself and try to solve its complexity! Don’t worry, there’s a solution manual should you get stuck and find you can’t quite manage it.

name: Mini Rubiks Cube 2x2x2
description: If you don't have any experience in the resolution of the Rubik's cubes, to learn how to solve the Mini Cube is a good start point.
